  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >95 New Levels: Tons of fresh and beautiful pictures to color. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Any Level, Anytime: Start with any level that catches your eye. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom Colors: Lots of shades to play around with. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chill Music: Relax with a soothing soundtrack while you color. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zoom In and Magnify: Perfect for those tiny details.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introducing a new cozy pixel coloring game, Paint by Pixel 3. It's the latest in the pixel painting series, and it's all about chilling out and enjoying some relaxing pixel art. With 95 brand-new images to color, there's plenty of coloring to do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/b604c23393bcada60b0692bed41ece13.poster.avif?t=1729574540\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/b604c23393bcada60b0692bed41ece13.webm?t=1729574540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/b604c23393bcada60b0692bed41ece13.mp4?t=1729574540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine sitting down with a cup of your favorite tea or coffee, putting on some comfy headphones, and getting lost in a world of colors. You don't have to follow any rules—just pick a picture that speaks to you, choose the colors you love, and start filling in those tiny squares. It's all about making each piece your own unique creation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/d8bf5bfdfdcf7045463678b2a69f7019.poster.avif?t=1729574540\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/d8bf5bfdfdcf7045463678b2a69f7019.webm?t=1729574540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/d8bf5bfdfdcf7045463678b2a69f7019.mp4?t=1729574540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paint by Pixel 3 is perfect for relaxing, unwinding, and expressing your creativity. It's like having a cozy little art studio right on your screen.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introducing a new cozy pixel coloring game, Paint by Pixel 3. It's the latest in the pixel painting series, and it's all about chilling out and enjoying some relaxing pixel art. With 95 brand-new images to color, there's plenty of coloring to do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/b604c23393bcada60b0692bed41ece13.poster.avif?t=1729574540\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/b604c23393bcada60b0692bed41ece13.webm?t=1729574540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/b604c23393bcada60b0692bed41ece13.mp4?t=1729574540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine sitting down with a cup of your favorite tea or coffee, putting on some comfy headphones, and getting lost in a world of colors. You don't have to follow any rules—just pick a picture that speaks to you, choose the colors you love, and start filling in those tiny squares. It's all about making each piece your own unique creation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/d8bf5bfdfdcf7045463678b2a69f7019.poster.avif?t=1729574540\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/d8bf5bfdfdcf7045463678b2a69f7019.webm?t=1729574540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463720/extras/d8bf5bfdfdcf7045463678b2a69f7019.mp4?t=1729574540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paint by Pixel 3 is perfect for relaxing, unwinding, and expressing your creativity. It's like having a cozy little art studio right on your screen.</p>",
